display="inline"><![CDATA[n\in \mathbb {N}]]></fr:tex>. Then the <fr:link
type="local"
href="nt-000J.xml"
addr="nt-000J"
title="Degree of extension">finite extension</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {F}_{p^{n}} / \mathbb {F}_{p}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
type="local"
href="nt-000N.xml"
addr="nt-000N"
title="Simple Field Extension">simple</fr:link>, which means there exists some irreducible polynomial <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f(x)\in \mathbb {F}_{p}[x]]]></fr:tex> of degree <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex> such that
<fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {F}_{p^{n}}\cong \mathbb {F}_{p}[x]/(f(x)).]]></fr:tex></fr:p>
 
   
